{"title":"“八大员”歌唱生产管理","authors":["张国富"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":7,"day":10}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"“八大员”歌唱生产管理"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哈尔滨庆华工具厂工人　张国富合唱："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌儿好唱口常开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱起歌儿干劲来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家齐心搞管理，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火旺人人来添柴。生产组长："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生产组长我担当，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遇事大家来商量，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人员、计划调配好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生产才能打胜仗。技术员："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"技术关键我不怕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工人阶级智慧大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"团结大家齐动手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高山也要挖掉它。核算员："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是工人核算员，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生产完毕把账翻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了成本再降低，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪怕算到黑了天。技安员："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"技安工作最重要，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人物都是国家宝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生产安全都做好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社会主义来得早。机电员："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"机器设备保管好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生产任务能确保，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱惜机床如眼睛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天天监督把油浇。工具员："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工具保管要妥当，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"严防腐蚀把锈上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"损坏工具找原因，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"逐步降低消耗量。材料员："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢铁材料要节约，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辅助材料少消耗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人动脑搞“利废”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"克勤克俭办法妙。定额员："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生产定额大家说，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我再逐道来琢磨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人插上“红一号”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工人领导笑呵呵。治保员："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"治安保卫最重要，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"安全生产要做好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"消除事故堵漏洞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阶级警惕要提高。结尾合唱："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工厂事情大家办，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两参一改好经验，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“脑力”“体力”不"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"分家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幸福乐园在眼前。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}